overview:
Al Gomez is an seo expert who is also maintaining his own blog at AlSEOBlog where he able to share what he had find out over the search engine. He also shares his own insights and some tips on search engine optimization. Passionately working for quality, he makes sure that the content he is going to share can be useful to the public. And to share the freshest information over the web he makes sure that he done several researches and also does some experiments.

Aside from blogging he is also the founder and the administrator of Dlinkers. You can know more about him or his work through his blog.
